column5: I started watching Jenny Graigs on tv right after eating all those christmas meals my wife and friends made and then lost 150 pounds in just two day . The buttons stay on my shirts now plus no body gets hurt and i don't pass out any more trying to tie my shoes , i feel great thanks to.... three more , two more , one more .... keep it up now !
Don't you wish those muscles were brains?
Well yes Roy , and i am already counting past three .
With a body like that, you'd get really cold really fast ice fishing.  Insulation has its benefits.  Just saying.
I for one can speak from experience here. Went from 230,down to 175,size 40 waist to a 36.. I got cold fast. Back to 190.and am good.
190 is a good weight Brian ,thats  some thing i wont see for a long time.
Thats because you cant see the scale when yer on it Ron  But thats ok.The Doc said i aint fat, just too short. A man my weight, should be 37 feet tall
That would be " eye of the beer holder"
